00:26.280 --> 00:30.080
Let's kick things off with the brand new Fedora 30 release.

00:30.080 --> 00:34.440
Yeah, no more cloud edition that's been merged with server, which seems quite logical to

00:34.440 --> 00:35.440
me.

00:35.440 --> 00:38.560
