01:54.540 --> 01:56.400
workstation edition.

01:56.400 --> 02:02.000
Top to bottom in every level of the project, they're really executing on this release.

02:02.000 --> 02:04.000
I've been really happy with Fedora 30.

02:04.000 --> 02:08.320
