03:09.120 --> 03:13.720
And I used to never say that about a Fedora release, so that's an accomplishment on its

03:13.720 --> 03:14.720
own.

03:14.720 --> 03:19.660
We really are spoiled for choice now, aren't we, with Ubuntu 19.04 and Fedora 30.

03:19.660 --> 03:24.160
