23:48.040 --> 23:50.600
You now have a support package backed by Canonical.

23:50.600 --> 23:54.920
Honestly, if I was still a consultant these days, I'd be installing Ubuntu like crazy

23:54.920 --> 23:57.000
and then selling it with this for each desktop.

